# Code owners for the StreetJS framework.
#
# Owners are auto-requested for review on PRs touching matching paths. Combined
# with branch protection ("Require review from Code Owners"), this is what lets
# the OpenSSF Scorecard "Code-Review" check credit changes as reviewed.
#
# NOTE: every rule currently resolves to @hassanmubiru (the only verified
# handle). A richer team-based version is staged in CODEOWNERS.proposed — replace
# the @org/*-team placeholders there with real teams, then move it over this file.
#
# Last matching pattern wins; specific rules come AFTER the catch-all.

*                                   @hassanmubiru

# ── CI / supply chain — highest scrutiny ───────────────────────────────
/.github/                                   @hassanmubiru
/.github/workflows/                         @hassanmubiru
/.github/workflows/publish-plugins.yml      @hassanmubiru
/.github/workflows/sign-htmx.yml            @hassanmubiru
/.github/workflows/block-private-keys.yml   @hassanmubiru
/.github/workflows/ci-cd.yml                @hassanmubiru
/.githooks/                                 @hassanmubiru
/.gitleaks.toml                             @hassanmubiru

